+/// Control characters are percent-encoded to prevent escape sequence injection:
+/// - C0 controls (U+0000-U+001F): Contains ESC (0x1B) and BEL (0x07)
+/// - DEL (U+007F)
+/// - C1 controls (U+0080-U+009F): Contains CSI (U+009B), ST (U+009C), OSC (U+009D)
